{"tid":2195869,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★2020-05-07 】金融科技(IT)三大入門職位 人工可達$3.5萬","createTime":"2020-09-09T12:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T07:27:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"093800d7884c08a207bf8a1019e6e2d3a6c89e3d","tid":2195869,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"2020-05-07 <br />\n<br />\n科技發展日新月異，為各行各業帶來轉變，其中金融業亦積極推動數碼轉型。雖然本港FinTech（金融科技）的發展仍然處於起步階段，但隨著FinTech對傳統銀行業的影響愈來愈大，尤其是政府已發出多個虛擬銀行牌照，行業的發展前景實不容忽視。一眾職場新鮮人，如果想投身金融科技行業，可以從以下入門職位入手：<br />\n<br />\n「金融科技」，顧名思義就是結合「科技」與「金融」，利用科技改善金融服務，提升用戶體驗等。金融科技的應用層面廣泛，不一定局限於銀行業，而是可以應用於零售、保險業等，但所涉及的工作大致離不開電腦工程、編碼、系統分析等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/article/%e7%95%a2%e6%a5%ad%e5%b0%b1%e6%a5%ad-%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e4%b8%89%e5%a4%a7%e5%85%a5%e9%96%80%e8%81%b7%e4%bd%8d-%e4%ba%ba%e5%b7%a5%e5%8f%af%e9%81%94-3-5%e8%90%ac/1235-20932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Farticle%2F%25e7%2595%25a2%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e5%25b0%25b1%25e6%25a5%25ad-%25e9%2587%2591%25e8%259e%258d%25e7%25a7%2591%25e6%258a%2580%25e4%25b8%2589%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2585%25a5%25e9%2596%2580%25e8%2581%25b7%25e4%25bd%258d-%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e5%258f%25af%25e9%2581%2594-3-5%25e8%2590%25ac%2F1235-20932&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg0YzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=d76ee1ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/article/%e7%95%a2%e6%a5%ad%e5%b0%b1%e6%a5%ad-%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e4%b8%89%e5%a4%a7%e5%85%a5%e9%96%80%e8%81%b7%e4%bd%8d-%e4%ba%ba%e5%b7%a5%e5%8f%af%e9%81%94-3-5%e8%90%ac/1235-20932</a>"},{"pid":"56021e47847801e7b241ba14ee3e192367636251","tid":2195869,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"h